  </header>
  <div id="map"
    <%- include('map.ejs') %>
  </div>
  <p id="offer-title"><i>Harmony in Darkness: AstroSentinel - Mapping Solutions for a Light-Pollution-Free Ecosystem<i></p>
  <section style="background-image: url('https://c.wallhere.com/photos/98/83/Bing_nature_landscape-2077985.jpg!d'); background-size: cover;" class="offer-item">
    <!-- Section 1 content goes here -->
    <h1 id="offer-title">About</h1>
    <p>Welcome to AstroSentinel, a platform dedicated to exploring and understanding light pollution's impact on our night sky. Our mission is to provide a space where enthusiasts, researchers, and concerned citizens can come together to contribute, learn, and raise awareness about the effects of light pollution.</p>
  </section>

  <section style="background-image: url('https://c.wallhere.com/photos/98/83/Bing_nature_landscape-2077985.jpg!d'); background-size: cover;">
    <!-- Section 2 content goes here -->
    <div id="what-we-offer">
        <h1 id="offer-title">What We Offer</h1>
        <div class="offer-item">
          <h3>1. Data Visualization</h3>
          <p> Explore interactive data visualizations depicting light pollution levels across different regions. Gain insights into the extent of artificial light and its impact on celestial visibility.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offer-item">
          <h3>2.Contribute Your Data</h3>
          <p> Become an AstroSentinel by contributing your own light pollution measurements. Help build a comprehensive dataset to further our understanding of how artificial light affects the environment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offer-item">       
          <h3>3. Learn and Educate</h3>
          <p>Access resources and guides on light pollution monitoring techniques. Learn why monitoring light pollution is crucial for preserving natural ecosystems and promoting sustainable lighting practices.</p>
          </div>
    </div> 
  </section>

  <section style="background-image: url('https://c.wallhere.com/photos/98/83/Bing_nature_landscape-2077985.jpg!d'); background-size: cover;">


    <div class="offer-item">
      <h1 id="offer-title">Log and Obtain Measurements</h2>

      <div class="offer-item">
        <h3>1. Why Contribute to AstroSentinel?</h3>
        <p>By contributing your measurements, you play a crucial role in:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>* Building a comprehensive database for researchers and enthusiasts.</li>
          <li>* Enhancing our understanding of light pollution's impact on the night sky.</li>
          <li>* Supporting global efforts to address light pollution and promote sustainable lighting practices.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>2. Obtain Measurements</h3>
        <p>Curious about light pollution levels in your area? Follow these steps to obtain measurements:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Step 1: Download a light meter app or use specialized equipment.</li>
          <li>Step 2: Find a dark location away from artificial lights.</li>
          <li>Step 3: Follow our <a href="/guide">guide page</a> to capture accurate measurements.</li>
          <li>Step 4: Contribute to AstroSentinel by submitting your findings.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
     
        <!-- Log Your Measurements -->
      <div>
        <h3>3. Log Your Measurements</h3>
        <ul>  
          <li>Step 1: Set up your equipment.</li>
          <li>Step 2: Choose a location with minimal light pollution.</li>
          <li>Step 3: Follow our guide to record accurate measurements.</li>
          <li>Step 4: <a href="/signup" >Sign up</a> on AstroSentinel.</li>
          <li>Step 5: <a href="/login">Log in</a> to AstroSentinel and submit your data.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

